<tr>
    <td>
        {issue:id=XXX-NNNNN|style=style}
    </td>

    <td>
        <p>Inserts link to YouTrack issue that changes its appearance depending on the issue state. Link tooltip
            provides issue details.</p>

        <ul>
            <li><b>id</b> &mdash; required. YouTrack issue id. For example, JS-2541.</li>
            <li><b>style</b> &mdash; optional. <i>detailed</i>> inserts issue title before the link, <i>short</i>
                (default) link only.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </td>
</tr>